{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was completely crazy with fear at this stage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a little cart, a kind of a-- just a cart, the horse cart belonging to the bakery, with-- with sliding doors-- wooden thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in my panic, I opened the sliding door and I hid inside the cart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was full of bread deliveries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It belonged to the bakery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I stayed there for some time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then after some time, I don't know how long, somebody opened it, and there was this man who was speaking to me and saying me who I was and where I came from and who was my father and if my father would give him money if I brought-- if he brought me to him, and I said of course, yes.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he was just somebody who lived in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took me to his flat, and he was so scared as well that he put me into the drawer of the chest of drawers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He put me into the drawer, and he closed the lock on this drawer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they were all completely crazy, because the Germans obviously had no time in searching this house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they would search the house, how would they know that I escaped out of there, that I was not his cousin or something like that?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But how would they know that I was already on the way to umschlagplatz?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But everybody was so scared out of their wits that they didn't know what they were doing anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started suffocating in this drawer, because there was air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I started hitting on the-- on there, and he luckily heard me.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
